<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40'>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Pakistan Visa Application Personal Info</title>
<style>
body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 15px; }
td { padding: 5px; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
.label { font-weight: bold; width: 160px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-right: 1px solid #ddd; }
.input { color: #000; padding-left: 10px; }
.section-header { background-color: #115740; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 8px; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.1em; border-radius: 4px; }
h1 { text-align: center; color: #115740; border-bottom: 3px solid #115740; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
p.intro { color: #666; text-align: center; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Pakistan Visa Application Form (파키스탄 비자 신청서)</h1>
<p class="intro">Please fill out this form in English or Korean. (본 양식을 영문 또는 국문으로 작성해 주세요.)</p>

<div class="section-header">1. Personal Information (인적사항)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Full Name (성명):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Name in Hanja (한자명):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Gender (성별):</td>
        <td class="input">M / F</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Date of Birth (생년월일):</td>
        <td class="input">YYYY-MM-DD</td>
        <td class="label">Nationality (국적):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Place of Birth (출생지):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(City, Province, Country)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Marital Status (결혼여부):</td>
        <td class="input">Married / Single / Divorced / Widowed</td>
        <td class="label">Religion (종교):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">2. Passport Information (여권 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Passport Number:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Place of Issue:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Date of Issue:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Date of Expiry:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">3. Work & Education (직업 및 학력)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Occupation (직업):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Company/School Name:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Phone Number:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Position (직위):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Address (직장 주소):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Highest Education (학력):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">High School / Bachelor / Master / Doctor (Major: _________________)</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">4. Family Members (가족 사항)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Father's Name:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Nationality:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Mother's Name:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Nationality:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Spouse's Name:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Nationality:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Children (자녀):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(Name, Gender, DOB)</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">5. Travel Information (여행 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Purpose of Visit:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">Tourism / Business / Family Visit / Transit</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Intended Arrival Date:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Intended Stay (Days):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Itinerary (Destinations):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Inviter (초청인/호텔):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(Name, Address, Phone Number in Pakistan)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Emergency Contact:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(Name, Relationship, Phone Number)</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div style="margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; page-break-inside: avoid;">
    <p>I declare that the information provided is true and correct.</p>
    <br>
    <p><strong>Date (신청일):</strong> _______________________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Signature (서명):</strong> _______________________</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
